reviewText: Absolutely loved it worth the money the DVD arrived on time and it was just as it was described for fans of rob van dam and the original ecw this is a must buy.
Everything came exactly how it was described

This another home run release from RF Video. This 6 disc collection features every RVD -Lynn match from their ECW run, including the "fan cam" matches shot at ECW live events. Also included are interviews and important angles in their rivalry. Picture quality varies on a few matches, but won't affect your viewing. If you're a hardcore fan, you won't be disappointed.
